<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ehliyet Cepte - İndir</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .app-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 24px; /* iOS tarzı yumuşak köşeler */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        p {
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .store-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .store-buttons img {
            height: 48px; /* İki butonun da aynı boyda görünmesini sağlar */
            width: auto;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .store-buttons img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Üzerine gelince hafif büyüme efekti */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <img src="app-icon.png" alt="Ehliyet Cepte İkonu" class="app-icon" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
    
    <h1>Ehliyet Cepte</h1>
    <p>Ehliyet sınavına hazırlanmanın en kolay yolu. Hemen indir, çıkmış sorularla çalışmaya başla!</p>
    
    <div class="store-buttons">
        <a href="SENIN_APP_STORE_LINKIN_BURAYA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="https://tools.applemediaservices.com/api/badges/download-on-the-app-store/black/tr-tr?size=250x83&amp;releaseDate=1276560000" alt="App Store'dan İndirin">
        </a>
        
        <a href="SENIN_PLAY_STORE_LINKIN_BURAYA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="en_badge_web_generic.png" alt="Google Play'den Alın">
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
